newsitem.title: LEBANON: Earth tremor rocks buildings in Lebanon.
newsitem.headline: Earth tremor rocks buildings in Lebanon.

text.p: A tremor shook buildings in Beirut and the southern Lebanese cities of Tyre and Sidon on Wednesday.
Residents in the fifth floor of a Beirut office building felt the floor shake. Reporters in Tyre and Sidon said buildings there also shook.
There were no immediate reports of damage or casualties and it was not known where the epicentre of the tremor was located.
The tremor was also felt in Cyprus and Egypt.
